metadata.name: Immortal
metadata.description:
She is a Queen of Fae.
She is the ancient one.
One of the elders of Gaia.
She remembers.

Immortal is channelled and encoded with energies for your own awakening in alignment with your best and highest good.

Connect with her every time you are being guided and allow the activation codes present to do their magic.

Love, Ashtara
